{"tid":1728650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TIME年度風雲人物要投！但儘投就ok","createTime":"2019-11-17T03:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T04:48:38.000Z","uid":3501,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6a015fca15c099701e09e082d5f198c4f821bb4f","tid":1728650,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:21:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://time.com/person-of-the-year-poll-2019/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2Fperson-of-the-year-poll-2019%2F&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUzwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=91d673cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://time.com/person-of-the-year-poll-2019/</a><br />\n俾多次link先<br />\n可能要幾個鐘後先有email 同埋當左垃圾郵件<br />\n<br />\n但想提下大家網上投票只供參考<br />\n最後決定權都係雜誌編輯群度嘅<br />\n<br />\n隔離post樓主之後搵左舊年網上投票都係bts<br />\n但舊年風雲人物都唔係bts啦<br />\n呢篇報導from台灣: <a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201812080024.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201812080024.aspx&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUzwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=692fc6a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201812080024.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2018年風雲人物係「真相守護者和事實之戰」（Guardians and the War on Truth）</strong><br />\n<br />\n咁其實大家唔洗話太絕望見到投左成日都無變<br />\n亦唔洗為呢件事嘈咁耐<br />\n努力投到top2/3都應該可以<br />\n集中火力去其他戰線！<br />\n<br />\n想上time都係想宣傳去國際線姐<br />\n留返啲氣力屌popo好過<br />\n唔好得罪bts 環保妹啲支持者好無<br />\n韓國人今次幫左好多架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a1520a99fada02b7ea9a0b0577ee97ef861cf6","tid":1728650,"uid":199709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6a015fca15c099701e09e082d5f198c4f821bb4f","tid":1728650,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:21:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://time.com/person-of-the-year-poll-2019/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2Fperson-of-the-year-poll-2019%2F&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUzwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=91d673cc\" d